<!--
    Demo / seed data for edu_academic_structure.
    Loaded with noupdate="1" so records are not overwritten on module upgrade.

    Scenario — Himalaya College of Science & Technology, Kathmandu:
      - 3 Departments: Computer Science, Management, Engineering
      - 5 Programs:
          BCS  = 4-year / 8-semester undergraduate (CS)
          BBA  = 4-year / 8-semester undergraduate (Mgmt)
          MBA  = 2-year / 4-semester postgraduate (Mgmt)
          BCE  = 4-year / 8-semester undergraduate (Eng)
          BIT  = 3-year / 6-semester undergraduate (CS)
      - Academic Year 2025-2026 (active) with 2 semesters
      - Academic Year 2026-2027 (draft, upcoming) with 2 semesters
      - 30+ subjects across departments
      - Curriculum mapped for first 2 semesters of each program
      - Batches for 2025-2026 with sections
-->
